# start-ocr

![Github CI](https://github.com/justmars/start-ocr/actions/workflows/main.yml/badge.svg)

## Development

See [documentation](https://justmars.github.io/start-ocr).

1. Run `poetry install`
2. Run `poetry shell`
3. Run `pytest` or:

    ```sh
    docker build --tag ocr . && docker run ocr
    ```

